  	<div class="word left">WEBESITY</div>
    <div class="right">
    <p class="pronunciation">[weh-bee-si-tee]</p>
  	<p class="type">[noun]</p>
    </div>
    <div class="left">
  <p class="definition">A condition that results from cramming too much information into a small screen:</p>
  <br>
  <p class="use"><i>webisty</i> often leads to frustrated customers, competitive disadvantage and loss of revenue.</p>
  </div>
