  <td>
  <div class="marketing">
  <p>Browsing the web on a mobile phone is often frustrating because most sites are webese.</p>
  <p>As a result, finding basic information like a phone number, business hours or an address involves an intricate sequence of pinching, zooming and scrolling in every direction until you find what you need.</p>
  <p>Webesity is more than an inconvenience, it <a href="/why-mobile">affects your bottom line</a>. When your site is webese, your mobile visitors will notice and many will turn away.</p>
  <p>Fixing this problem used to be expensive and a lot of hard work, but not anymore, so you can relax.</p>
  <p>We designed Yomobi to make it fast and easy for you to create your own mobile-friendly site. We organize all your information in such a way that it is easy for your mobile vistors to find what they need with only one move: a tap. They don't have to pinch and zoom. We like to think of ourselves as the one stop shop for 'tap-friendly' sites.</p>
  <p>Our platform really is simple. If you can drag-and-drop and cut-and-paste, you can create your own beautiful mobile site in 5 minutes.</p>
  <p>Join Yomobi's tap my site campaign by <a href="/users/sign_up">signing up today</a>, and together we can put an end to websity.</p>
